      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-text-primary mb-3">What We Provide</h2>
        <p>NailTheQuote provides free online calculators, estimators, templates, and business tools designed for home service professionals. All tools are provided as-is for informational and estimation purposes only.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-text-primary mb-3">Not Professional Advice</h2>
