        <p>We make reasonable efforts to ensure our calculators use accurate formulas and current industry data. However, we do not guarantee the accuracy, completeness, or reliability of any calculation, estimate, or output. You are responsible for verifying all results before using them in professional work, customer quotes, or business decisions.</p>
      </section>

