          <li>Scrape, copy, or reproduce our tools or content for use on another website.</li>
          <li>Use automated systems to access the site in a way that degrades performance for other users.</li>
          <li>Misrepresent NailTheQuote outputs as certified engineering, legal, or financial documents.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
